Enrique Guitart https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Enrique_Guitart 0 Enrique Guitart (May 1, 1909 – November 30, 1999) was a Spanish stage and film actor. He appeared in around forty films during his career. He was the son of an actor of the same name. Enrique_Guitart ( May_1_,_1909 – November_30_,_1999 ) was a_Spanish_stage_and_film_actor .
